title: Jamie Dornan Dishes on 'Incredible' Masquerade Scene in 'Fifty Shades Darker' (Video)
text:
Jamie Dornan and Dakota Johnson are opening up about the masquerade scene in their movie Fifty Shades Darker for this new featurette!
“The masquerade ball lends a sense of mystery to the film and it is so massive and the colors are really saturated,” Dakota says in the video that debuted on Marie Claire .
“The masquerade ball is something thrown by Christian’s parents for charity and it just looks incredible,” Jamie adds.
The book’s author E.L. James , who produced the movie, said, “It’s lavish. It’s sensuous. And it looks fabulous. It’s the sort of place where you think, ‘I wish I was there.’”
Make sure to see Fifty Shades Darker when it hits theaters on February 10 to watch the scene!
